Happened long time ago ♪</i>

01:10:16.212 --> 01:10:21.434
<i>♪ Little bitty pretty one
I've been watchin' you grow ♪</i>

01:10:21.968 --> 01:10:25.939
<i>That was my personal favorite played
especially for all you little bitty pretty ones</i>

01:10:26.097 --> 01:10:27.815
<i>moving and grooving
on this sunny afternoon.</i>

01:10:27.974 --> 01:10:31.228
<i>Playing music to make you smile,
so you'd better not touch that d--</i>

01:10:43.489 --> 01:10:45.287
Shouldn't we have a search
warrant to do this?

01:10:45.450 --> 01:10:47.828
No, this guy's dirty.

01:10:47.994 --> 01:10:51.874
Once we show this tape in court,
Wormwood's goose is cooked.

01:10:52.039 --> 01:10:55.589
I'm sure that box is full
of stolen car parts.

01:10:55.835 --> 01:10:57.678
You've been taping all week.

01:10:57.837 --> 01:11:00.681
How about letting me handle
that camera for a while?

01:11:00.840 --> 01:11:02.592
You know how to use it?

01:11:02.759 --> 01:11:05.353
You know about the zoom
and the white balance?

01:11:05.511 --> 01:11:09.482
You know how to adjust the eyepiece?
I can handle it.

01:11:12.727 --> 01:11:15.196
Besides, it's my turn.

01:11:15.354 --> 01:11:17.948
Yeah, your turn to drop it.

01:11:18.107 --> 01:11:20.860
I won't drop it.

01:11:21.027 --> 01:11:22.745
Come on.

01:11:23.154 --> 01:11:27.204
You two men are gonna be
in a lot of trouble very soon.

01:11:27.366 --> 01:11:30.040
It's the female minor.

01:11:31.329 --> 01:11:33.172
Aren't you supposed
to be in school, young lady?

01:11:33.331 --> 01:11:35.379
I really hope you have
a search warrant.

01:11:35.541 --> 01:11:38.841
According to a constitutional
law book I read in the library,

01:11:39.003 --> 01:11:43.383
if you don't have one, you could lose
your job or even go to federal prison.

01:11:43.800 --> 01:11:45.723
It's your father who's
going to federal prison.

01:11:46.010 --> 01:11:49.059
And you know where you'll end up?
In a federal orphanage.

01:11:49.222 --> 01:11:51.645
If you cooperate, we'll make
sure it's a nice orphanage.

01:11:52.016 --> 01:11:56.066
The kind with food
and teeny-weeny cockroaches.

01:11:56.229 --> 01:11:57.276
What do you say?

01:11:58.731 --> 01:12:03.487
There's another crime in the making.
Your car's about to run a stop sign.

01:12:14.664 --> 01:12:18.259
<i>So she bought a little time
for her dad to come to his senses.</i>

01:12:18.417 --> 01:12:21.421
<i>But now Matilda had
bigger fish to fry,</i>

01:12:21.587 --> 01:12:23.635
<i>much bigger.</i>

01:12:38.187 --> 01:12:41.942
Hey, dip-face,
where are you going?

01:12:42.108 --> 01:12:44.156
Out.

01:12:46.445 --> 01:12:49.949
Hey, dip-face, have a carrot.

01:13:03.296 --> 01:13:06.140
Chew your food.
You're an animal.

01:13:11.470 --> 01:13:13.472
<i>Having power
isn't nearly as important</i>

01:13:13.639 --> 01:13:15.562
<i>as what you choose to do with it.</i>

01:13:15.725 --> 01:13:19.901
<i>And what Matilda had in mind
was nothing short of heroic.</i>

01:14:44.146 --> 01:14:46.990
Come here. Come on.
Lissy Doll, come on.

01:14:47.149 --> 01:14:50.153
Come, Lissy. Come on, doll.
Please. Come on.

01:14:50.319 --> 01:14:52.447
Come on, Lissy.
Please come here.

01:15:08.295 --> 01:15:09.797
Yes!

01:16:53.192 --> 01:16:55.536
Leave me alone!

01:17:29.353 --> 01:17:31.401
Magnus!

01:18:30.623 --> 01:18:35.094
Miss Honey! Miss Honey,
you'll never believe what I got you.

01:18:36.295 --> 01:18:38.639
Oh, Matilda.

01:18:39.381 --> 01:18:42.305
Matilda.
Oh, I also brought you this.

01:18:42.468 --> 01:18:44.311
I ate mine last night.

01:18:58.901 --> 01:19:02.201
I will be teaching
your class today.

01:19:08.494 --> 01:19:11.873
<i>In the time it took Miss
Honey to get very, very nervous,</i>

01:19:12.039 --> 01:19:15.088
<i>Matilda had formulated a plan.</i>

01:19:15.542 --> 01:19:18.011
She is really raving mad.

01:19:18.170 --> 01:19:21.595
What is it your father used to call you?
Hummingbird?

01:19:21.757 --> 01:19:25.261
Bumblebee. I'm sure
she knows the doll's missing.

01:19:25.427 --> 01:19:27.304
And he called her
Trunchbull?

01:19:27.471 --> 01:19:31.101
No, I suppose he called her
Agatha. Yes, that's--

01:19:31.267 --> 01:19:35.488
She called him Magnus, right?
Yeah. Yes.

